title: Episode 230: Anything But Fake Polo (Feat. Styles P & Adjua)

description:
Styles P and his lovely wife Adjua join the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote Adjua's book "The Ethereal Hike." The ladies cover a range of topics including peeing the bed, boxers vs briefs, leaving the toilet seat up, and much more. Enjoy!
